## Original Content by Robert Murray-Smith

This bot queries an archive of Robert Murray-Smith's publicly available work.
Robert's original content is shared under the licenses he chose:

- **3D Models (Thingiverse):** [Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 (CC BY 4.0)](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)
- **YouTube Videos:** YouTube standard license

